						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up near the well at the entrance to the village.</p>						

						<p>1194 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1117, Ānanda, Chaitra ba. 2, Saturday, corresponding to 1194 A.D., April 9. The Śaka year was current.</p>						

						<p>It records the death of the grand-mother of Peṇḍara Bāchi, who was a devotee of the god Tīrthachandraprabha.</p>						

						</summary>
